dialogues.text: What the hell is that in front of me?

Analyzing environment...
New surface detected.
Classification: soft... not penetrable.
So... what am I supposed to do with this?

It has properties similar to rebound materials
known on your planet. If you impact it from a
certain distance, you should...

Rebound?
Are you telling me I can rebound?!

Affirmative. The strength of the rebound will
depend on the height and speed of the impact.

Reminder: abilities have multiple applications.
Do not limit yourself to a single approach.

I like how you think... or whatever you do before...
speaking?

Before initiating the rebound, make sure to
check what's in your trajectory.
